Invocation Name: calorie count
des: Instantly get calorie count on almost any food! Just say Alexa, Calorie Count. More than one food? Easy. The conversation continues - just say another food and Alexa says the calories without needing to restart. Use Calorie Count to quickly & easily get calorie information.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
